{"tid":2050241,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【八仙塵爆】500人傷亡現場淪探險廢墟 倖存者煉獄中重生不敢重回","createTime":"2020-06-04T04:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T09:25:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"df48379284735b097c123ce13872460290232d82","tid":2050241,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T04:14:58.000Z","msg":"距台灣八仙水上樂園粉塵爆炸慘劇5周年尚有約3星期，這宗造成15人身亡，逾484人受傷的事故，才終於有首名受害者獲法院判賠。曾被新北市寄望帶動當地旅遊的八仙樂園，在天文賠償陰霾下淪為廢墟。有倖存者雖然熬過痛不欲生的治療，積極展開新生，仍不敢重臨八仙舊地，害怕勾起當日煉獄般的可怕回憶。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JXLLD4LZAZ4EWLWYYWXOXP57LY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJXLLD4LZAZ4EWLWYYWXOXP57LY.jpg&h=59605ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文link<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200604/6T5LV26D73YJC7FXFMM5MPGWEY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200604%2F6T5LV26D73YJC7FXFMM5MPGWEY%2F&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=d1977b85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200604%2F6T5LV26D73YJC7FXFMM5MPGWEY%2F&h=973732de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200604/6T5LV26D73YJC7FXFMM5MPGWEY/</a>"},{"pid":"dbd3f95676e4247c16d37ca0870768fb352e7f1a","tid":2050241,"uid":140953,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"佢個樣冇事都幾好彩"},{"pid":"91a5b57cbddb98e803c9bcb8a96b9777393ff51e","tid":2050241,"uid":321345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dbd3f95676e4247c16d37ca0870768fb352e7f1a","tid":2050241,"uid":140953,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"佢個樣冇事都幾好彩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T04:23:21.000Z","msg":"個身一撻撻都死"},{"pid":"ae346caf61789f65bdf613d82f18e6adf0c04600","tid":2050241,"uid":49336,"